# Sentinel file — do not edit or remove.
#
# When a new repository is created from `hourloop/agent-template`,
# the presence of this file in the first push triggers
# `.github/workflows/init.yml`. That workflow substitutes
# `{{AGENT_NAME}}` / `{{AGENT_DESCRIPTION}}` placeholders from the
# new repo's name + description, then deletes itself, this sentinel,
# and `TEMPLATE.md`.
